mAtRubhrAtRuvihiMsakO&pi satataM bhOgaikabaddhAdaraH |
nityaM stOtramidaM japan raghupatiM bhaktyA hRudisthaM smaran
dhyAyan muktimupaiti kiM punarasau svAchArayuktO naraH || 23 || 

